title: Harry Frankfurt, philosopher of excrement-level falsehoods, dies at 94
description: Dr. Frankfurt’s bestselling book, with a title referencing a form of deceit that employs a word bleeped out during his many TV interviews, earned him literary fame.

title: Facebook will make its latest AI model free to use
description: The social media giant is doubling down on its open source approach on Llama, in contrast to Google, Microsoft and OpenAI.

title: U.S. blacklists spyware companies, citing security threats
description: Intellexa and Cytrox were added to a federal “entity list” that prohibits American companies from engaging in certain trade activities with them.
